  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `v1.9.0`\r\nOS & Version: Linux/OSX (container)\r\nDocker images: ethereum/client-go:v1.8.27 & ethereum/client-go:v1.9.0\r\n\r\nSpotted by @pdobacz. Memory usage is significantly higher with v1.9.0 vs v1.8.27. Both instances were serving no RPC requests when the below outputs were taken.\r\n\r\n#### v1.8.27\r\n\r\n`docker run -d --entrypoint /bin/sh ethereum/client-go:v1.8.27 -c geth --dev --dev.period 1`\r\n\r\nAfter 15 minutes:\r\n\r\n```\r\nCONTAINER ID        NAME                CPU %               MEM USAGE / LIMIT     MEM %               NET I/O             BLOCK I/O           PIDS\r\n264d11d1015f        sharp_leakey        17.43%              258.2MiB / 1.952GiB   12.92%              13.4MB / 2.99MB     23.2MB / 16.4kB     12\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### v1.9.0\r\n\r\n`docker run -d --entrypoint /bin/sh ethereum/client-go:v1.9.0 -c geth --dev --dev.period 1`\r\n\r\nAfter 15 minutes:\r\n\r\n```\r\nCONTAINER ID        NAME                CPU %               MEM USAGE / LIMIT     MEM %               NET I/O             BLOCK I/O           PIDS\r\n827aab4dea99        frosty_noether      125.79%             1.653GiB / 1.952GiB   84.68%              178MB / 31.7MB      283MB / 1.22GB      12\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n",
